des:
Do you like challenges!?
Let's have a challenge in Mathematics.
Division Game challenges your math skills in dividing two numbers. You'll be given two random numbers to divide. Then, you shall be asked to respond with the division result. Practice your division skill with Alexa. It is not necessary but if you play this game on an Echo Show 10 device (3rd Gen), you get some cool motion responses.
